# Fast-path coverage allowlist — grandfathered zero-coverage names.
# Generated: 2026-04-23T09:00Z from the coverage baseline.
# See docs/maintenance.md for how to shrink this list.
#
# Rules enforced by tests/fast_path_coverage.rs:
#   - Entry appears here AND is in the src detect_* registry AND the
#     corpus does not hit it  → grandfathered (tolerated, not failing)
#   - Entry appears here but the src registry no longer has it  → FAIL
#     (stale entry — delete it)
#   - Entry appears here AND the corpus does hit it  → FAIL
#     (no longer needs grandfathering — delete to keep the list shrinking)
#   - A new detect_* path in src with zero corpus hits and not here  → FAIL
#     (add a probe in the same PR, or add the name here with a comment)
#
# Blank lines and #-prefixed comments are ignored.

